FOAD
1. [[System of a Down|Faggots of a down]], a band that caught an [[extreme|3xtreme]] case of teh [[ghey]].

2. Fuck Off And Die

3. An e-dialect that is more [[Engrish]] than [[English]]. Usually involves avoiding capitalising letters and not using proper punctuation, coupled with atrocious spelling. Perpetrators of [[FOAD]] seem to think 'tehy r teh [[1337]]', but sadly, they are nothing more than [[teh]] [[ghey|gh3y]].

The real hardcore FOAD [[fags|fellas]] use a lot of those annoying faggotted images called [[emoticon]]s, and can hold a conversation using nothing but these pictures, much like chimpanzees - except [[moron|without teh gr3y matter]]. 


